China Buys Net 345.6 Billion Yen Short-Term Japan Debt in August

-- B y   M o n a m i   Y u i
-- 
2011-10-10T23:59:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/china-buys-net-345-6-billion-yen-short-term-japan-debt-in-august.html
China bought a net 345.6 billion yen
($4.5 billion) in Japanese short-term maturity debt in August,
according to a statement released by Japan’s Ministry of Finance
in  Tokyo  today. China was a net seller of 166.7 billion yen in
medium- and long-term bonds, today’s data also showed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Naoto Hosoda at 
 nhosoda@bloomberg.net  